{"tid":1245756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根據警察通例  警察係唔可以阻住人使用救護服務","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T09:57:53.000Z","uid":20818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e65f2c44ef0dfc52ec7a98c7c4f09b3b9dacf2a","tid":1245756,"uid":20818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"頭先留意到<br />\n警察通例27-02<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">救護車到達現場時，在場的警務人員須讓救護人員立即將假定仍有生命的受害人送院救治；又如在場的警務人員斷定受害人已經死亡，則須通知救護人員離去。</span><a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo027.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo027.pdf&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D7zLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=8a30b46f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo027.pdf</a><br />\n而香港法例亦都賦予消防處喺發生火警或其他災難時趕走班警察<br />\n發生火警時消防處的權力<br />\n發生火警或其他災難時，處長或主管消防處或消防處任何分隊的其他成員可 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<br />\n為保障人命財產，採取他覺得必需或合宜的措施；<br />\n(b)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">移走或命令他統率的成員移走任何干擾消防處操作的人，不論該人是以在場或以行動而干擾</span>；<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap95!zh-Hant-HK?INDEX_CS=N&amp;xpid=ID_1438403573315_004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap95%21zh-Hant-HK%3FINDEX_CS%3DN%26xpid%3DID_1438403573315_004&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D7zLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=dd560403\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap95!zh-Hant-HK?INDEX_CS=N&amp;xpid=ID_1438403573315_004</a><br />\n聽日大家唔舒服可以放心叫救護車<br />\n有錯請法律JJ指正<br />\nBTW<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日一定要出嚟呀!</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nqk7x8h6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnqk7x8h6&h=f55d940e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e92d8a58c8723470fcb30b9a482263d78beced0","tid":1245756,"uid":134149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔就快比警察更熟識警察通例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d02c48d2d45434a36c47b67d52f37a53ebaca","tid":1245756,"uid":136729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}